    "lines": [
        {
            "text": "(soft music)",
            "time": 1.49
        },
        {
            "text": "- I have a problem.",
            "time": 2.44
        },
        {
            "text": "You see,",
            "time": 5.18
        },
        {
            "text": "in a time before memory existed",
            "time": 7.82
        },
        {
            "text": "out of nothing,",
            "time": 9.307
        },
        {
            "text": "(exploding sound)",
            "time": 10.290
        },
        {
            "text": "a universe was created.",
            "time": 12.01
        },
        {
            "text": "So big.",
            "time": 13.2
        },
        {
            "text": "So massive.",
            "time": 14.271
        },
        {
            "text": "It's impossible to comprehend in any meaningful way.",
            "time": 19.573
        },
        {
            "text": "And in one small corner",
            "time": 22.33
        },
        {
            "text": "of that",
            "time": 23.984
        },
        {
            "text": "vast,",
            "time": 24.913
        },
        {
            "text": "vast universe",
            "time": 25.746
        },
        {
            "text": "through pure chance",
            "time": 28.762
        },
        {
            "text": "and the great infiniteness of time,",
            "time": 30.913
        },
        {
            "text": "a proliferation of life emerged.",
            "time": 33.36
        },
        {
            "text": "Life that would eventually become us.",
            "time": 35.527
        },
        {
            "text": "For most of our existence",
            "time": 38.780
        },
        {
            "text": "we knew little of the details of exactly",
            "time": 41.640
        },
        {
            "text": "how we were created.",
            "time": 44.090
        },
        {
            "text": "Until one day, our knowledge",
            "time": 46.55
        },
        {
            "text": "our technologies allowed us to discover the building blocks.",
            "time": 50.150
        },
        {
            "text": "for life itself.",
            "time": 52.250
        },
        {
            "text": "And in the blink of an eye",
            "time": 54.04
        },
        {
            "text": "we went from mapping our creation to editing it.",
            "time": 57.913
        },
        {
            "text": "Giving us the power to not only create life",
            "time": 64.170
        },
        {
            "text": "but to control it.",
            "time": 65.333
        },
        {
            "text": "Making us the gods",
            "time": 67.860
        },
        {
            "text": "of our",
            "time": 68.890
        },
        {
            "text": "and others",
            "time": 71.630
        },
        {
            "text": "destiny",
            "time": 73.363
        },
        {
            "text": "and the moral dilemmas",
            "time": 76.07
        },
        {
            "text": "that arise from this",
            "time": 79.86
        },
        {
            "text": "may be the biggest humanity has ever faced.",
            "time": 84.713
        },
        {
            "text": "So today",
            "time": 87.22
        },
        {
            "text": "I ask you",
            "time": 89.743
        },
        {
            "text": "what role genetic engineering should play",
            "time": 93.55
        },
        {
            "text": "in the development of our unborn children.",
            "time": 98.133
        },
        {
            "text": "(soft music)",
            "time": 101.484
        }
    ]
